item.title: astroworld exclusive ride time
item.description: 26 September 1998 Today I was frustrated (again) at my computer so I decided to go to Astroworld. I have a season pass and I’ve hardly used it; I think this is my 3rd time to go this season. (Strictly speaking I’ve gotten my money’s worth out of it, but only 3 times??) I’m pretty much tired as heck, so I’ll keep this short. I got there around 4pm and paid my 5 bucks to park.
